    "description": "In this cooperative roguelike action adventure game, choose a class and play with up to 4 players as ice cream dogs Neo, Coby, Chaz and Miley. Venture through the Savage Garden and ascend the Dark Tower to defeat the Calico King. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/f10f03d654e949f1e41c15e938939827.avif?t=1770339786\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/84fb7d9da7ee5a77a55cef8a4cd1b460.poster.avif?t=1770339786\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/84fb7d9da7ee5a77a55cef8a4cd1b460.webm?t=1770339786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Each run presents new puzzles, enemies, skills and items to discover. As you advance, the Tower and the King grow stronger, offering fresh challenges with every playthrough.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/4c65e2eba6f60811d61c228c9a277bcc.avif?t=1770339786\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/9ee8fe12572c652558c41d54419fee38.poster.avif?t=1770339786\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/9ee8fe12572c652558c41d54419fee38.webm?t=1770339786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Battle your way through hordes of enemies and bosses, each with their own set of unique attacks and abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/5a39a992f1623f20e130790cf5023a4f.avif?t=1770339786\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/69cdf4bda30bdd5615092b6db26f4be1.poster.avif?t=1770339786\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/69cdf4bda30bdd5615092b6db26f4be1.webm?t=1770339786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Each class has their own unique set of skills and upgrades that vary from run to run. Try out different combinations to find the best build for your play style. Uncover the Tower's secrets unlock new powers to aid future runs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/6dc1b259d6b6e4193dc6c9dfd2865dfc.avif?t=1770339786\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/8e7fdadc03b10a000d21ed10fb0678c2.poster.avif?t=1770339786\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/8e7fdadc03b10a000d21ed10fb0678c2.webm?t=1770339786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/8e7fdadc03b10a000d21ed10fb0678c2.mp4?t=1770339786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Team up with up to four players. Work together to defeat enemies, solve puzzles, and play minigames.",
